    <string name="help_center_title">Help Center</string>
    <string name="help_center_faq_header">Frequently Asked Questions</string>
    <string name="help_flame_bubble_collapsed">Hi! I&apos;m Flame.\nHow can I help you?\nTap on a card to see details.</string>
    <string name="help_flame_bubble_expanded">Yes, exactly! If you don&apos;t find the answer here, tap on me – we&apos;ll solve it together.</string>
    <string name="help_flame_cd">Flame Assistant</string>
    <string name="help_no_email_app">No email app found</string>
    <string name="help_email_subject">Question for Flame</string>

    <string name="help_q1_title">How to find a parish on the map?</string>
    <string name="help_q1_desc">Use the magnifying glass icon in the top right corner to type a city or parish name. You can also tap the [icon] icon in the side panel to instantly center the map on your location.</string>

    <string name="help_q5_title">What if I don&apos;t want to share my location?</string>
    <string name="help_q5_desc">Sharing location is not mandatory, but without it, the app won&apos;t show your position on the map or automatically indicate the nearest Mass. Your location is used solely for map navigation and is not collected or used by us in any other way.</string>

    <string name="help_q6_title">How to find the nearest Mass?</string>
    <string name="help_q6_desc">Below your position button, there is a [icon] icon. Tapping it opens a card with the nearest services and options to &apos;Navigate&apos; or &apos;Remind&apos;.</string>

    <string name="help_q7_title">How to set a Mass reminder?</string>
    <string name="help_q7_desc">Tap the &apos;Nearest parish&apos; button, then choose the Mass time you are interested in. Tap the &apos;Remind&apos; button and specify how many minutes before the service we should notify you.</string>

    <string name="help_q8_title">How do I turn off a reminder?</string>
    <string name="help_q8_desc">Open the side menu (hamburger icon), select &apos;Settings&apos;, and then &apos;Manage List&apos; in the notifications section. You can remove any reminder by tapping the trash can icon.</string>

    <string name="help_q9_title">How to add a new parish that is not listed?</string>
    <string name="help_q9_desc">You can do this in two ways: long-press on the map where the church is located and select &apos;Add parish here&apos;, or use the &apos;+&apos; button in the side menu and fill out the form manually.</string>

    <string name="help_q10_title">What is the Intention Wall for?</string>
    <string name="help_q10_desc">It&apos;s a place for worldwide communal prayer. You can ask for support here or join in praying for others. You choose the form of prayer – from a short &apos;Our Father&apos; to a full Rosary or Novena.</string>

    <string name="help_q11_title">How to share an intention on Facebook?</string>
    <string name="help_q11_desc">Open the Intention Wall from the side menu. Next to your intention, you will find a share button. Choose a background that fits your request, tap &apos;Share image&apos;, and select the Facebook app.</string>

    <string name="help_q12_title">Can I add a Polish parish from abroad?</string>
    <string name="help_q12_desc">Yes, absolutely! The Your Parish app is global. You can add Roman Catholic parishes from every corner of the world – from Chicago to Oslo or Sydney.</string>

    <string name="help_q13_title">I am a pastor – how can I manage my parish in the app?</string>
    <string name="help_q13_desc">The ability to add official Mass intentions and announcements by the parish is arranged individually. Please contact us at biuro.mojaparafia@gmail.com – we will prepare a cooperation offer.</string>

    <string name="help_q14_title">How do I check my points and rewards?</string>
    <string name="help_q14_desc">You can check your Ambassador points in the side menu. 10 pts gives you &apos;Crown&apos; status (highlights your intentions), 50 pts is &apos;Premium&apos; status (removes ads), and 200 pts gets you a free t-shirt from us!</string>

    <string name="help_q15_title">What if I see incorrect Mass times?</string>
    <string name="help_q15_desc">If you spot an error, go to the parish details and tap the &apos;Suggest a change&apos; button. Your report will be verified, and after the data is corrected, you will receive an Ambassador point from us!</string>

    <string name="help_q16_title">How to quickly return to my parish?</string>
    <string name="help_q16_desc">In the parish details, tap the [icon] icon. The parish will be added to your favorites, giving you quick access via the map&apos;s side panel (heart icon).</string>

    <string name="help_q17_title">Is the app paid?</string>
    <string name="help_q17_desc">Using the Your Parish app is completely free. Displayed ads help us cover server costs. If you want to turn them off for free, just earn 50 Ambassador points!</string>

    <string name="help_q18_title">What is the Home Parish for?</string>
    <string name="help_q18_desc">Thanks to this, the name of the parish from which the intention was sent appears on the Intention Wall. This helps build a local community within our global prayer space.</string>

